    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the vegetables are in the oven, add the<strong> diced chicken thigh</strong> to a medium bowl with the <strong>remaining five-spice mix</strong>, 2/3 of your <strong>cornflour </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together – this is your <strong>coated five-spice chicken</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1682601384183-x200.jpg",
