    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>five-spice vegetables</strong> from the oven and add the <strong>crispy five-spice chicken </strong>with the <strong>remaining chicken stock mix</strong></p><p>Mix everything together until fully coated – this is your <strong>five-spice chicken, peppers & chips</strong></p>",
